OL,3,CMan jailed after fire at illegal tyre
OL,4,Cdump shut schools
OL,6,FThe "reckless" owner of an an illegal
OL,7,Fwaste site has been jailed ` four
OL,8,Fyears after a fire huge fire forced
OL,9,Fnearby schools to close.
OL,11,FNearly 100 firefighters were called to
OL,12,Fa fire in Bradford in 2020, when a
OL,13,Fblaze spread through the site on
OL,14,FSpring Mill Street where over 600,000
OL,15,Ftyres were being stored.
OL,17,FMore than 14,300 children were
OL,18,Fimpacted by school closures and the
OL,19,Fnearby railway line was disrupted for
OL,20,Fseveral days.
