OL,3,CMan jailed after fire at illegal tyre
OL,4,Cdump shut schools
OL,6,FPeople living in the East Bowling area
OL,7,Fwere instructed to keep their doors
OL,8,Fand windows shut.
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency had served an
OL,11,Fenforcement notice ordering the owners
OL,12,Fto clear the tyres a month earlier.
OL,14,FStuart Bedford, 62, formerly of
OL,15,FHarrogate, pleaded guilty to operating
OL,16,Fwaste sites in Bradford and Doncaster
OL,17,Fwithout the required environmental
OL,18,Fpermits.
OL,20,FHe was sentenced to a year in prison.
