OL,3,CMan jailed after fire at illegal tyre
OL,4,Cdump shut schools
OL,6,FHis wife, Vicky Bedford, 51, was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 12-month community order
OL,8,Fand 15 days rehabilitation activity
OL,9,Frequirement for her involvement at the
OL,10,Fsites.
OL,12,FThe Bedfords were arrested in Spain
OL,13,Fafter international arrest warrants
OL,14,Fwere issued.
OL,16,FThe Environment Agency said both
OL,17,Foperations caused "unacceptable
OL,18,Fdisruption" to local people and risk
OL,19,Fto the environment.
