OL,6,FHis Honour Judge Gibson told Stuart
OL,7,FBedford: "You know from an early stage
OL,8,Fthat the number of tyres you stored on
OL,9,Fthe site was vastly more than you
OL,10,Fwould have been legitimately able to
OL,11,Fstore under an exemption issued for
OL,12,Fthat site.
OL,14,F"As far as the fire itself is
OL,15,Fconcerned, you were reckless in the
OL,16,Fstandard meaning of that word.
